---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Technology - intelio">
<main>
  <!-- HERO SECTION WITH BACKGROUND IMAGE -->
  <section class="hero-technology min-h-screen flex items-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Image/Video -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900" style="z-index: 0;">
      <!-- You can add a video or image here for technology/infrastructure/systems architecture theme -->
    </div>
    
    <!-- Dark Overlay for text readability -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30 z-[1]"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.1] tracking-[-1px] text-white mb-6">
          Technology
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-4">
          Built to support real businesses, not demos.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-white/60 mb-8">
          Technology only creates value when it aligns with how a business actually operates.
        </p>
        <a href="#philosophy" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
          See Our Approach
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Opening Statement -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          At intelio, technology is not the product — it's the infrastructure that makes execution reliable, scalable, and visible.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          We design, integrate, and operate systems that sit underneath revenue, operations, finance, and decision-making — applying AI and automation only where it creates real leverage.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Our Philosophy -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100" id="philosophy">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Our Philosophy</p>
      
      <!-- Bold Statement -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">
          Technology should disappear into the business.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Most organizations don't fail because they lack tools. They fail because tools are fragmented, poorly integrated, or misaligned with how work actually happens.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Framework (3-step approach) -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Our approach is simple:</p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">1</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Business intent first</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">2</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Systems second</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">3</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Technology last</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Principle Callout -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium leading-relaxed">
          We do not chase trends, ship novelty, or deploy AI for optics. Every system we build must support execution, reduce friction, or improve decision quality.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: The Intelio Operating Layers (Centerpiece) -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">The Intelio Operating Layers</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-16 max-w-3xl">
        Rather than selling tools, we architect operating layers that work together.
      </p>

      <!-- Layer 1: Core Business Systems -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-8 border border-gray-200">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Core Business Systems</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 mb-6">These are the systems your teams touch every day.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>CRM and revenue systems</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Operations and workflow management</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Scheduling, dispatch, and execution tooling</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Accounting, billing, and financial control</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">We design these systems around actual workflows, not software defaults.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Layer 2: Automation & Integration Layer -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-8 border-2 border-blue-200">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Automation & Integration Layer</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 mb-6">This is where fragmentation disappears.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Workflow orchestration across tools</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Event-driven automation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Data synchronization and validation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Notifications, alerts, and handoffs</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Audit and compliance logging</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">This layer ensures information moves cleanly across the organization — without manual effort.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Layer 3: Intelligence & AI Layer -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-8 border border-gray-200">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Intelligence & AI Layer</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 mb-4">AI is applied selectively, not universally.</p>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-700 mb-6">We deploy intelligence where it meaningfully improves outcomes:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Lead prioritization and routing</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Forecasting and scenario modeling</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Cost and margin anomaly detection</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Document analysis and abstraction</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Decision support and summarization</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">AI is embedded into workflows — not bolted on as a separate experience.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Layer 4: Visibility & Decision Layer -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-gray-200">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Visibility & Decision Layer</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 mb-6">Executives need clarity, not dashboards for dashboards' sake.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Real-time performance visibility</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>KPI standardization across departments</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Drill-down from summary to transaction</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Early warning signals for risk and variance</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">This layer turns data into decisions — not reports.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Platforms We Standardize On -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Platforms We Standardize On</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl">
        We work with proven, enterprise-grade platforms to ensure durability, security, and scalability.
      </p>

      <!-- Enterprise Foundations -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 mb-6">Enterprise Foundations</h4>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Microsoft</h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Identity, automation, data, AI, and enterprise infrastructure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Google</h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Workspace, analytics, search, and local presence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic text-center">These platforms form the backbone of many systems we deploy.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Business Systems & Tooling -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 mb-4">Business Systems & Tooling</h4>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mb-6">Depending on the organization, systems may include:</p>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>CRM and revenue platforms</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Accounting and financial systems</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Operations and scheduling tools</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Data warehouses and reporting layers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Automation and integration frameworks</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic mt-6">We select tools based on fit, maturity, and operational reliability, not hype.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Configured, Not Fragile -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Configured, Not Fragile</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">intelio configures proven systems to your business.</p>

      <!-- "We do not" list -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-8">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-6">We do not:</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Build fragile one-off stacks</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Reinvent commodity software</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Experiment on production businesses</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Positive statement -->
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium">
          Customization happens through architecture, integration, and workflow design, not brittle code.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Custom & Advanced Technology Projects -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Custom & Advanced Technology Projects</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">In select cases, off-the-shelf tools are not sufficient.</p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mb-12">For organizations operating at scale or complexity, we undertake custom system design and advanced AI-enabled projects, including:</p>

      <!-- Feature cards -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Internal platforms and proprietary tooling</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Specialized data and decision workflows</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Cross-department intelligence systems</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Advanced automation and orchestration</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">AI-driven analysis and decision support</h4>
        </div>
